<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<style>
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;}
body{width:1200px;height:630px;overflow:hidden;}
@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@700;900&family=Noto+Serif+JP:wght@600;900&display=swap');
.bg{width:1200px;height:630px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#111010 0%,#1c1b1b 100%);display:flex;align-items:center;padding:72px;position:relative;}
.grid{position:absolute;inset:0;background-image:linear-gradient(rgba(200,224,107,0.04) 1px,transparent 1px),linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(200,224,107,0.04) 1px,transparent 1px);background-size:48px 48px;}
.content{position:relative;z-index:1;}
.tag{display:inline-block;background:rgba(200,224,107,0.15);border:1px solid rgba(200,224,107,0.3);color:#c8e06b;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;padding:5px 18px;border-radius:4px;letter-spacing:0.12em;margin-bottom:24px;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;}
.title{font-family:'Noto Serif JP',serif;font-size:56px;font-weight:900;color:white;line-height:1.2;margin-bottom:20px;}
.title em{color:#c8e06b;font-style:normal;}
.sub{font-size:20px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);margin-bottom:40px;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;line-height:1.6;}
.stats{display:flex;gap:40px;}
.stat .num{font-family:'Noto Serif JP',serif;font-size:36px;color:#c8e06b;font-weight:900;line-height:1;margin-bottom:4px;}
.stat .lbl{font-size:13px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4);font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;}
.logo{position:absolute;bottom:40px;right:72px;font-family:'Noto Serif JP',serif;font-size:20px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.3);}
.logo strong{color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="bg">
  <div class="grid"></div>
  <div class="content">
    <div class="tag">AI Marketing Automation</div>
    <div class="title">AIで、中小企業の<br>マーケティングを<em>再設計</em>する。</div>
    <div class="sub">月1回30分のインタビューで、コンテンツを全自動生成。</div>
    <div class="stats">
      <div class="stat"><div class="num">10本</div><div class="lbl">ブログ記事/月</div></div>
      <div class="stat"><div class="num">30分</div><div class="lbl">月の作業時間</div></div>
      <div class="stat"><div class="num">30日</div><div class="lbl">無料トライアル</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="logo">Mimosa<strong>Works</strong></div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
